01:04.107 --> 01:05.527
<i>...in the night.</i>

03:41.055 --> 03:42.765
Don't shoot me.

03:49.981 --> 03:51.611
Who is that?

03:51.983 --> 03:54.743
There's your money. Release the hostages.

03:54.944 --> 03:55.954
How much in there?

03:56.029 --> 03:59.779
