- You're too late. We want $5 million.

04:01.743 --> 04:03.243
Fuck, it's humid!

04:07.457 --> 04:08.457
Last chance!

04:09.250 --> 04:10.250
Take it or leave it.

04:10.627 --> 04:11.627
All at ease!

04:13.296 --> 04:14.416
Take a seat, Gunner.

04:15.131 --> 04:16.881
Hey, you're all cannon and no balls!

04:17.133 --> 04:19.343
We want the money now!

04:20.887 --> 04:22.137
- Warning shot.
- No!

04:26.309 --> 04:27.309
A little low

04:34.192 --> 04:35.232
Lights out!

05:05.515 --> 05:08.095
I'll kill him! I swear I'll kill him!

05:08.518 --> 05:11.188
If I were you,
I'd take this opportunity to leave.

05:12.188 --> 05:13.478
What's your call? You stayin'?

05:17.360 --> 05:18.570
Yeah, we tried.

05:18.653 --> 05:20.953
I'll kill them all! I don't care.

05:21.030 --> 05:23.870
There's more fools in this world
than people. So back off, cuz.

05:24.158 --> 05:25.278
You back off!

05:26.035 --> 05:29.615
You know, you're gonna be dead anyway.
So I'm gonna shut up.

05:30.748 --> 05:32.958
Last chance. Let the hostages go

05:34.460 --> 05:35.550
or you're out of there.

05:35.628 --> 05:37.838
Bring the money here to me.

05:38.256 --> 05:39.716
I need the money myself.

05:41.592 --> 05:43.092
I'll take the four on the left.

05:43.219 --> 05:44.179
Oh, here we go.

05:44.262 --> 05:46.472
Why don't you take the two on the right
and leave the rest alone?

05:46.556 --> 05:47.716
I'll kill them all!

05:47.849 --> 05:50.389
You should take the two on the right.
You're not that fast any more.

05:50.852 --> 05:52.352
The only thing faster is lightning.

05:53.479 --> 05:55.569
"Light!" Get original!

05:57.400 --> 05:59.860
Bullets go faster than blades.

06:00.611 --> 06:01.611
We'll see.

06:02.780 --> 06:04.530
Bring the money here! Now!

06:04.991 --> 06:06.411
You want the money?

06:08.578 --> 06:09.618
Go get it.

06:09.912 --> 06:11.582
Kill them!

06:17.628 --> 06:19.958
- I call that a tie.
- Come on, keep dreaming.

06:20.089 --> 06:21.799
A little compassion, folks.

06:22.008 --> 06:23.508
You know, I don't think
you hit one of them.

06:24.010 --> 06:25.340
I don't see any knives, actually.

06:27.346 --> 06:29.096
Three million doesn't buy much nowadays.

06:29.432 --> 06:30.682
How are you guys doing?

06:33.561 --> 06:35.861
- What the hell is he doing?
- Hanging a pirate.

06:36.189 --> 06:37.519
Don't be ridiculous.

06:38.649 --> 06:41.279
Gunner! What are you doing?

06:41.778 --> 06:43.278
Hanging a pirate!

06:43.946 --> 06:46.736
- That is seriously demented.
- This is no good.

06:46.949 --> 06:49.449
Not that you'd feel it,
but put one in Speed Racer's shoulder.

06:49.619 --> 06:51.449
- You're on your own.
- Appreciate it.

06:51.621 --> 06:53.121
It's good to have friends.

06:53.247 --> 06:54.957
- Gunner.
- Yeah?

06:55.041 --> 06:57.291
This isn't how we work. Let him go.

06:57.543 --> 06:59.553
Why? He'd do it to us.

07:00.004 --> 07:02.054
You know what you're doing
is a little crazy, right?

07:02.131 --> 07:03.131
That's his problem.

07:03.382 --> 07:05.302
It's your problem, too. It's a little sick.

07:08.387 --> 07:10.597
Hey, don't touch my money.

07:11.349 --> 07:13.019
Gunner, last chance.

07:13.101 --> 07:15.021
Let him go or we're letting you go.

07:15.228 --> 07:17.558
It's good to hang pirates.
Old Viking custom.

07:17.897 --> 07:19.857
It isn't an old Viking custom at all.

07:38.334 --> 07:39.674
