- Everyone does.

07:57.895 --> 07:59.145
Let him go, Gunner.

07:59.230 --> 08:00.360
Let him go?

08:01.482 --> 08:02.532
Let him go.

08:20.209 --> 08:22.549
- Think he's cool?
- Go.

08:38.102 --> 08:39.232
Gunner, you cool?

08:42.523 --> 08:43.523
Yeah.

08:55.369 --> 08:56.579
No, keep it.

08:58.080 --> 08:59.710
You appreciate a good blade.

13:16.755 --> 13:17.755
Coming!

13:21.218 --> 13:22.298
Who is it?

13:22.386 --> 13:25.966
Someday you'll find a man
who'll be happy just to watch you sleep.

13:30.394 --> 13:33.194
- Hi. I didn't know you were back.
- Hey, babe.

13:34.482 --> 13:36.282
Yeah, I just arrived.

13:36.400 --> 13:38.530
- Hey.
- You look great.

13:39.487 --> 13:41.277
I wish you would have called.

13:41.363 --> 13:43.413
I've never been a good caller.

13:44.366 --> 13:46.286
I haven't heard from you in over a month.

13:46.368 --> 13:48.788
Really? Time flies, huh?

13:49.246 --> 13:51.036
Won't happen again! Sorry.

13:51.540 --> 13:54.790
But I do have a surprise.

13:55.377 --> 13:57.877
Rose-flavored. Your favorite.

13:58.380 --> 14:02.220
And I did have something else for you.

14:04.386 --> 14:08.716
It's something I picked up from Burma.

14:09.016 --> 14:10.386
It's a ruby.

14:12.394 --> 14:15.734
It's a good color,
but it's hard to see in this light.

14:15.856 --> 14:20.436
This kind of looked a little shinier
when I bought it in the shop, you know?

14:20.986 --> 14:23.406
Lace, everything all right?

14:27.076 --> 14:28.866
- Yeah.
- Who is he?

14:30.913 --> 14:31.963
He's a friend.

14:32.122 --> 14:34.332
Kind of late. You got a name?

14:37.586 --> 14:39.586
Friend. She just told you.

14:42.258 --> 14:43.378
Lee, come on.

14:43.467 --> 14:45.887
Don't leave like this. Lee, I'm sorry.

14:46.345 --> 14:47.885
I thought things were good between us.

14:47.972 --> 14:51.272
