15:15.416 --> 15:19.036
You bring me presents.
They're beautiful presents but I want you!

15:19.420 --> 15:21.340
You're a good man. I love you, but...

15:21.422 --> 15:23.972
- Lace!
- I hate his voice.

15:24.091 --> 15:26.511
- Did you say something?
- Don't let him come down here.

15:26.594 --> 15:27.644
Did you say something?

15:27.845 --> 15:30.845
- Do not let...
- Paul, just give me a second, okay?

15:38.022 --> 15:41.362
Lee, I'm sorry.

15:42.443 --> 15:44.193
Please tell me you understand
what I'm saying.

15:44.278 --> 15:47.158
- You have to understand.
- I understand.

15:49.074 --> 15:51.204
- You take care.
- Take care.

15:55.998 --> 15:57.248
He's no good, Lace.

16:35.746 --> 16:37.206
Hey, brother, don't you ever sleep?

16:39.792 --> 16:42.382
This is my friend...

16:43.504 --> 16:44.554
What's your name again, baby?

16:44.755 --> 16:46.045
- Cheyenne.
- Cheyenne.

16:46.131 --> 16:48.221
Cheyenne, Arapaho, Cherokee, Pawnee.

16:49.218 --> 16:50.218
You want a drink?

16:50.761 --> 16:51.761
I'm good.

16:53.222 --> 16:54.852
Why don't you run upstairs

16:54.932 --> 16:59.232
and get me one of them
super-duper six-olive martinis, baby?

16:59.311 --> 17:00.981
- Anything for you, baby.
- You got it.

17:03.107 --> 17:05.397
- Got a crush on me.
- Like the last 50.

17:05.567 --> 17:07.107
Hey, brother, who's counting?

17:07.194 --> 17:09.824
- Damn, you look good.
- Look at you.

17:09.905 --> 17:11.865
You look like a goddamn
cold piece of steel, brother.

17:11.949 --> 17:16.249
Yeah, well.
Okay, my friend, let's finish this bird up.

17:16.745 --> 17:20.365
Well, let's do it, bro. It's taken you
