17:23.794 --> 17:25.924
We had to get rid of Gunner.

17:26.463 --> 17:29.683
Well, he went Crankenstein on your ass.
You got to cut him loose.

17:29.842 --> 17:31.052
You wanna fill in?

17:31.760 --> 17:32.850
Let me tell you something.

17:32.928 --> 17:34.808
Remember where we was last time?

17:34.930 --> 17:36.720
Where were we?
We were ass-deep in that mud and blood.

17:36.807 --> 17:40.137
- Nigeria.
- Yeah, your hand was all shot to shit.

17:40.894 --> 17:43.314
You were bleeding all over the place,
and I was bleeding,

17:43.397 --> 17:45.897
and you know what I did?
I promised myself,

17:46.942 --> 17:50.362
I don't wanna die all alone,
full of holes in the mud and blood.

17:51.989 --> 17:54.449
I'm gonna die with something that counts.
I'm gonna die with a woman.

17:54.616 --> 17:57.866
I wanna die with someone
who cares about me, you know.

17:58.370 --> 17:59.960
I don't wanna die for a woman.

18:00.080 --> 18:02.120
I wanna die laying next to a woman.
That's what I want.

18:04.793 --> 18:07.133
- It's Christmastime.
- Yeah, I can smell him from here.

18:13.594 --> 18:15.604
Mr. Christmas. How you doing, brother?

18:17.431 --> 18:18.931
I'm good, Tool.

18:19.725 --> 18:20.725
How's the missus?

18:22.227 --> 18:23.517
Yeah, all good.

18:24.438 --> 18:25.438
Oh, good.

18:26.774 --> 18:28.784
So, take a look. What do you think?

18:31.987 --> 18:33.817
It still looks like a black chicken.

18:35.199 --> 18:37.329
Black chicken?

18:38.327 --> 18:42.537
Man. It's good to see you, brother. Miss you.

18:43.040 --> 18:45.330
You're looking very beige tonight.
What's up?

18:45.667 --> 18:46.747
The usual.

18:46.835 --> 18:48.795
- All good?
- Yeah.

18:49.046 --> 18:50.416
I got a great idea.

18:50.506 --> 18:53.086
Why don't you let me doodle, like, a...

18:53.467 --> 18:55.797
Charlotte's web on your head?
On the top of your head.

18:55.886 --> 18:57.506
You know, something different,
something exciting.

18:57.596 --> 19:00.466
'Cause you got one of them
perfectly-shaped domed, muscular heads.

19:00.641 --> 19:04.561
I could put a web on the top of the head.

19:05.145 --> 19:07.895
Maybe a pregnant Charlotte
coming out of your ear,

19:07.981 --> 19:11.321
peeking around,
making sure them bugs don't come inside.

19:11.568 --> 19:13.858
Her long leg dangling down your neck.

19:14.196 --> 19:16.696
- Yeah. Sexy, right?
- Very sexy.

19:18.075 --> 19:19.075
