19:19.326 --> 19:23.116
Well. Okay, I'll tell you what.
I'm feeling a little lucky tonight.

19:23.539 --> 19:25.959
I'm feeling very accurate.

19:26.041 --> 19:28.881
- Another time. Come on.
- Come on, take him on.

19:29.086 --> 19:30.876
Come on, Christmas. Bring it, baby.

19:30.963 --> 19:32.343
Don't encourage him, please.

19:32.422 --> 19:33.512
He never beat you in your life.

19:33.590 --> 19:35.880
Come on, Christmas, no disgrace in losing.

19:50.732 --> 19:51.942
Yes?

19:56.029 --> 19:57.109
Yeah.

19:59.116 --> 20:00.236
Okay.

20:03.245 --> 20:05.245
Well, I got three pieces of work.

20:06.081 --> 20:09.881
Two a walk in the park,
and one to hell and back.

20:10.085 --> 20:12.745
- I need some time alone.
- Hey, cheer up. Make the meeting.

21:51.520 --> 21:53.690
Now we can see inside of him.

21:54.648 --> 21:56.688
And I see lies.

21:58.026 --> 22:01.696
He wasn't stealing from you.
He was stealing from us both.

22:03.156 --> 22:06.326
You want your apes' respect?
Snuff those two.

22:19.923 --> 22:21.433
Let's just keep it simple.

22:21.508 --> 22:23.678
If the money's right,
we don't care where the job is.

22:23.760 --> 22:25.760
- Got it?
- Let's quit jerking off

22:25.887 --> 22:27.717
get down to business, see who's hungry.

22:27.848 --> 22:30.228
I know your real name's
probably not Barney Ross.

22:30.809 --> 22:32.689
You don't need to know my name.

22:32.769 --> 22:36.229
The only thing you need to know is
the job's real and the money's real.

22:36.356 --> 22:38.726
But since we're in this nice place,

22:39.901 --> 22:42.151
you might as well just call me Mr. Church.

22:43.155 --> 22:45.065
Okay, Church. What can I do for you?

22:45.699 --> 22:48.579
In a minute.
I'm still waiting for one more guy.

22:48.702 --> 22:49.752
Who?

23:01.715 --> 23:02.715
You know him?

23:02.799 --> 23:04.759
Yeah, we used to be
on the same team together.

23:04.926 --> 23:06.796
What's my oldest, worst friend doing here?

23:07.095 --> 23:09.425
Both of your names came
to the top of the list.

23:09.890 --> 23:11.770
- Is that a problem?
- Yeah.

23:11.933 --> 23:13.773
Should've shot him when I had the chance.

23:13.935 --> 23:15.225
Big Barney Ross.

23:15.687 --> 23:17.307
Bigger Trench mouse.

23:17.689 --> 23:20.779
- What are you doing? Praying for work?
- Could be.

23:20.901 --> 23:22.151
Have you been sick?

23:22.402 --> 23:24.532
- You've lost weight.
- Really?

23:24.780 --> 23:27.200
Whatever weight I lost, you found, pal.

23:28.909 --> 23:31.239
You guys aren't gonna start sucking
each 0ther's dicks, are you?

23:36.666 --> 23:39.336
Let's get down to business,
see who wants the work.

23:39.795 --> 23:41.375
You ever hear of an island called Vilena?

23:41.463 --> 23:43.013
- No.
- Yeah.

23:45.008 --> 23:46.378
It's a little island in the Gulf.

23:46.635 --> 23:47.635
That's right.

23:47.969 --> 23:50.349
- You should read more.
- Thanks.

23:52.265 --> 23:55.265
There are resources on that island
that my people are very interested in.

23:55.477 --> 23:58.897
But a general by the name of Garza
has overthrown the half-ass government.

23:59.314 --> 24:00.774
That's right.

24:01.775 --> 24:04.025
My people are having a problem
with this fanatic Garza.

24:04.361 --> 24:06.321
- So you want Garza gone?
- I want him dead.

24:06.822 --> 24:08.412
All it takes is a little army.

24:08.490 --> 24:09.870
Only an idiot would do this job.

24:10.325 --> 24:12.445
- How much?
- Oh, like I said.

24:15.831 --> 24:18.541
I'm busy anyway,
so give this job to my friend here.

24:18.667 --> 24:20.167
He loves playing in the jungle.

24:20.293 --> 24:21.673
- Right?
- Right.

24:21.753 --> 24:24.303
Hey, why don't we have dinner?

24:24.422 --> 24:25.512
Sure. When?

24:25.841 --> 24:27.841
- In a thousand years.
- Too soon.

24:31.012 --> 24:33.682
- What's his fucking problem?
- He wants to be president.

24:37.435 --> 24:38.935
I got to recon this island first.

24:39.354 --> 24:41.024
I'll have a contact for you on the island.

24:43.567 --> 24:44.567
Good riddance.

24:45.443 --> 24:47.493
I got a feeling everyone else
has passed on this job,

24:47.571 --> 24:49.701
so our fee is $5 mil.

24:49.990 --> 24:52.700
-$5 mil?
- And I want half upfront,

24:52.784 --> 24:54.294
and the other half in an offshore account.

24:54.369 --> 24:57.539
- You got a problem with that?
- No.

24:58.665 --> 25:02.495
What I have a problem with
is people who try to fuck me over.

25:04.921 --> 25:08.341
So if you take this money
and you don't deliver,

25:09.968 --> 25:12.388
me and my people

25:12.470 --> 25:15.600
are gonna come get you and your people

25:15.682 --> 25:20.232
and chop you up
into little fucking dog treats.

25:21.688 --> 25:22.808
You got a problem with that?

25:29.279 --> 25:30.199
Let's talk.

25:46.254 --> 25:47.764
Whoever stood you up sounds bad.

25:48.048 --> 25:49.218
Yeah, but it will pay good.

25:49.591 --> 25:51.681
Yeah, well, money aside.
What happened to your code?

25:51.760 --> 25:52.760
What code's that?

25:53.094 --> 25:54.974
"The target has to deserve it."

25:56.014 --> 25:57.934
That was canceled due to lack of interest.

25:59.684 --> 26:03.524
- You're dark. Dark and cold.
- You noticed.

26:04.272 --> 26:06.272
- And I ain't buying into that, by the way.
- You will.

26:09.861 --> 26:12.241
Stick around, young man, you will.

26:17.452 --> 26:18.662
Vilena.

26:25.961 --> 26:26.961
Next job?

26:29.214 --> 26:30.344
They got work there?

26:34.552 --> 26:35.802
Come on.

26:36.304 --> 26:37.854
You know you shouldn't be here, Gunner.

26:38.223 --> 26:39.853
Don't replace me.

26:41.268 --> 26:42.308
I'm good.

26:43.895 --> 26:45.435
I'm still good.

26:46.064 --> 26:47.444
You're still using.

26:47.565 --> 26:49.145
