27:03.999 --> 27:05.209
You can't trust me?

27:14.592 --> 27:15.892
Be careful.

27:15.969 --> 27:17.429
You threatening me, Gunner?

27:19.180 --> 27:22.060
Nah, I'm a nice guy.

27:31.359 --> 27:33.649
So, going over the info
this guy Church gave me,

27:33.737 --> 27:36.607
there's probably about
6,000 people on the island.

27:37.073 --> 27:38.203
How many soldiers?

27:38.533 --> 27:39.663
Maybe a couple of hundred.

27:41.328 --> 27:43.828
It wouldn't take much more than that
to control a space that small.

27:44.080 --> 27:45.080
You do know that.

27:45.790 --> 27:47.830
Great, they've got a small army.

27:48.126 --> 27:49.166
What do we got?

27:49.419 --> 27:50.499
Four and a half men.

27:51.463 --> 27:53.303
That smells disgusting.

27:54.090 --> 27:56.800
Disgusting? Chicken gumbo is bad,

27:57.218 --> 28:00.678
but eating on rats and gorilla nipples,
that's delicious?

28:01.431 --> 28:02.521
Not so funny.

28:03.558 --> 28:05.098
- I need a raise.
- Why?

28:05.185 --> 28:06.765
I need more money for my son.

28:06.895 --> 28:08.555
I want to send him to a better school.

28:08.897 --> 28:11.067
- Did Yin Yang get a family?
- I have no idea.

28:11.149 --> 28:13.029
You don't ask, I don't tell.

28:13.443 --> 28:16.243
Anyway, the pay share stays the same.

28:17.197 --> 28:18.447
That's the way it's gonna be.

28:18.615 --> 28:21.025
Now the target on this island
is a guy named General Garza.

28:21.242 --> 28:24.082
- What's the problem?
- Who gives a shit what the problem is?

28:24.746 --> 28:26.826
We got enough problems
right here of our own.

28:26.998 --> 28:29.958
We don't get rid of those first,
they're gonna get rid of us.

28:30.377 --> 28:33.087
Toll Road, when was
the last time you saw your analyst?

28:35.340 --> 28:37.260
