- Yeah? What'd you talk about?

28:40.261 --> 28:42.431
Avoidant personality disorder.

28:42.597 --> 28:43.637
You think too much.

28:43.765 --> 28:47.515
You know, Toll Road, you're a great guy,
a little fucked up, no doubt about it,

28:47.602 --> 28:49.402
and you're always gonna have
unusual problems, right?

28:49.479 --> 28:51.649
